<plot>Two out-of-towners take an automobile tour of Hollywood to see the private lives of some celebrities. They (and we) see 'Reginald Denny (I)' (qv) at his model airplane factory; 'Clark Gable' (qv) at his farm; and 'Robert Young (I)' (qv), 'Allan Jones (I)' (qv) and 'Irene Hervey' (qv) at their horse stables. The visit ends at a celebrity baseball game, where they see the proverbial "galaxy of stars."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?243283</url></doc>
